# SerializationError.notRepresentableAsCoreML(debugDescription:)

**Case**

An error that indicates that the transformer cannot be represented as a CoreML model.

## Declaration

```swift
case notRepresentableAsCoreML(debugDescription: String)
```

## Analyzing the error

- **SerializationError.packageAlreadyExists(_:)**: An error that indicates that the package already exists at the URL.
- **SerializationError.packageNotFound(_:)**: An error that indicates that the package at specified URL was not found.
